<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912624>
    dc:description "FIGURE 44. Eugenia stigmatosa DC.: A. “Sellow 272” (K000276494). B. Sellow s.n. (S05-3051). C. Sellow 5929 (P05322198). D. Sellow s.n. = Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 687 (P05322199). Source: K (A), S (B), P (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912624/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912520>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Persea obovata Nees & Mart. A. Sellow B 1363 c 394, holotype (B 10 0185211). B. Sellow B 1363 c 394, isotype (B 10 0185210). C. Escola Polytechnica 696, Anonymous 103 = Sellow B 1363 c 394 (LISU [24018]). D. HERB. Dr.A. R. FERREIRA 696 ex LISU [24018] (K). Source: B (A, B), LISU (C), K (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912520/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912626>
    dc:description "FIGURE 45. Isotypes of Aulomyrcia acrantha O.Berg: A. Sellow 2743 = Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 1334 (P00549002). B. Sellow s.n. = “Rio Grande 1334” (R [163625; 2 exsiccatae]). Source: P (A), R (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912626/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912570>
    dc:description "FIGURE 22. Labels of specimens from the Province of Mato Grosso, with vernacular names of species and “N 148” and “N.o 104”. Source: P." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912570/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912628>
    dc:description "FIGURE 46. List of species sent by Silva Manso to Martius, dated May 30, 1833; 11-page manuscript listing 148 sequentially numbered species:A. Page 1, where the common names “Timbouva”, “Cotocoto” and “Pitomba” are indicated. B. Page 7, with an indication of three species of Copaifera under the numbers 95, 96 and 97, which were used by Martius (1837–1841) in the Herbarium Florae Brasiliensis, respectively under the numbers Martii Herbar. Florae Brasil. No 204 (as Copaifera martii Hayne), Martii Herbar. Florae Brasil. No 205 (as Copaifera elliptica Mart.) and Martii Herbar. Florae Brasil. No 203 (as Copaifera nitida Mart. ex Hayne). Source: Martius: Elenchus Nr. 390, Botanic Garden Meise." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912628/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912630>
    dc:description "FIGURE 47. Dipteracanthus geminiflorus var. hirsutior Nees: A. Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 51 (P03047385; síntipo), annotated “242” in the upper left corner of the label. B. duplicate of the Paris specimen (GZU000249554). Stenandrium pohlii var. pusillum Nees: C. Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 55 (P03584627; syntype), annotated “245” in the upper left corner of the label. D. duplicate of the Paris specimen (GZU000250379). Source: P (A, C), GZU (B, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912630/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912632>
    dc:description "FIGURE 48. Copaifera elliptica Mart.:A. Silva Manso 95 = Martii Herbar. Florae Brasil. No 204 (BR0000008445230). B. Silva Manso 96 = Martii Herbar. Florae Brasil. No 205 (BR0000009198081), holotype. C. Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 231 (P00481386). D. Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 287 (P00481387). Source: BR (A, B), P (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912632/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912634>
    dc:description "FIGURE 49. Copaifera elliptica Mart.: A. Martii Herbar. Florae Brasil. No 205 (M0215231 [F neg. 6206]), isotype. C. Riedel 750 (NY01921760). D. Riedel 750 (NY01921761). Copaifera malmei Harms: B. Malme I 1344 (S14-45416), isotype. Source: M (A), S (B), NY (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912634/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912638>
    dc:description "FIGURE 50. Ficus pertusa L.f.: A. Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 274 (P06753717). B. Herbier Impérial du BRÉSIL N.o 278 (P06753713). C. “Minas M. Gr. 274” (R010024082). D. “Minas M. Gr. 278” (R010024081). Source: P (A, B), R (C, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912638/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7912640>
    dc:description "FIGURE 51. Campylopus griseus (Hornsch.) A.Jaeger: A. Specimen with label “Rio Grande 55” mounted together with specimen from Sellow d 659 (R000083786). Campylopus filifolius (Hornsch.) Mitt.: B. “S. Paulo 14” (R000083787). Source: R." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7912640/files/figure.png" ;
